                                <condition>The inscription is damaged and weathered. The B-surface of the inscription is nearly all chipped away. A hole has been bored through the stone (at the current lower right hand angle) at some point subsequent to the carving of the inscription, as it mutilates one of the letters.</condition>
                            </supportDesc>
